104.6	A_Beautiful_Mind_(film)	A Beautiful Mind (film)	A Beautiful Mind is a 2001 American biographical drama film based on the life of John Nash, a Nobel Laureate in Economics. The film was directed by Ron Howard and written by Akiva Goldsman. It was inspired by a bestselling, Pulitzer Prize-nominated 1998 book of the same name by Sylvia Nasar. The film stars Russell Crowe, along with Ed Harris, Jennifer Connelly, Paul Bettany and Christopher Plummer.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/98/Abeautifulmindposter.jpg/220px-Abeautifulmindposter.jpg
